Package com.orsoncharts.label

Classes related to chart labels.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CategoryItemLabelGenerator
    An item label generator for category charts (this is used for tooltips and data item labels).
    CategoryLabelGenerator
    A label generator for category charts, used to create labels for the axes and for the chart legend.
    PieLabelGenerator
    A label generator for pie charts.
    XYZItemLabelGenerator
    A label generator for data items in XYZ charts (this can be used for tooltips and item labels).
    XYZLabelGenerator
    A label generator for XYZ charts, used to create labels for the chart legend.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    StandardCategoryItemLabelGenerator
    A default implementation of the CategoryItemLabelGenerator interface.
    StandardCategoryLabelGenerator
    A default implementation of the CategoryLabelGenerator interface.
    StandardPieLabelGenerator
    A default implementation of the PieLabelGenerator interface.
    StandardXYZItemLabelGenerator
    A default implementation of the XYZItemLabelGenerator interface.
    StandardXYZLabelGenerator
    A default implementation of the XYZLabelGenerator interface.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ItemLabelPositioning
    An enumeration of the item label positioning types.
